OL,3,CScotland could be thawing out the
OL,4,Ccouncil tax freeze
OL,6,FAfter the prime minister warned of
OL,7,F"painful" decisions lying ahead in the
OL,8,Fautumn, Scotland First Minister John
OL,9,FSwinney said he will be forced to make
OL,10,Fhundreds of millions of pounds worth
OL,11,Fof cuts to his own budget this year.
OL,13,F"We've got to face up to some very
OL,14,Fchallenging circumstances," he told
OL,15,FITV News in an interview on Thursday,
OL,16,Fahead of the SNP conference this
OL,17,Fweekend.
OL,19,F"(It is) arising mainly out of the
OL,20,Feffect of inflation on our budget,"
OL,21,Fthe first minister explained.
