OL,6,F"We've had sky high inflation, and
OL,7,Fwhat that does is undermine the value
OL,8,Fof public finances we've got
OL,9,Favailable."
OL,11,FBut economic inflation may not be the
OL,12,Fonly contributing factor. Scotland
OL,13,Falso has a notably inflated public
OL,14,Fsector when compared to the rest of
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,FScotland has a bigger public sector
OL,18,Fworkforce per capita than anywhere
OL,19,Felse in the UK, and has the highest
OL,20,Fcapital spending per capita.
