OL,3,CScotland could be thawing out the
OL,4,Ccouncil tax freeze
OL,6,FAnd the Scottish public sector is
OL,7,Falready paid more than the rest of the
OL,8,FUK, taking up a significant chunk of
OL,9,Fthe money available to the Scottish
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FThe independent Scottish Fiscal
OL,13,FCommission has already said the
OL,14,FScottish government is to blame for
OL,15,F"much of the pressure" on the public
OL,16,Ffinances currently.
OL,18,FThey say this, in large part, comes
OL,19,Fdown to public sector pay deals in
OL,20,FScotland being more generous than
OL,21,Fother parts of the UK.
