OL,7,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,8,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,9,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,11,FAnd yet, when I asked Mr Swinney about
OL,12,Fthis, he was adamant he doesn't see
OL,13,Fmerit in cutting the public sector to
OL,14,Fmake the necessary savings.
OL,16,FIn fact, he wants his public sector
OL,17,Fpaid more to help build "a high wage
OL,18,Feconomy", in his words.
OL,20,FSo, where does that leave the Scottish
OL,21,Fgovernment in terms of options?
