OL,3,CScotland could be thawing out the
OL,4,Ccouncil tax freeze
OL,6,FThey don't have borrowing powers. They
OL,7,Fcannot run a fiscal deficit under the
OL,8,Frules of devolution so they are
OL,9,Flegally obliged to balance the books.
OL,11,FWhat they do have is power to raise
OL,12,Ftax.
OL,14,FThe Scottish government has already
OL,15,Fraised taxes to a level that now means
OL,16,Fanyone earning more than #26,562 in
OL,17,FScotland pays more income tax than
OL,18,Fthey would if they lived elsewhere in
OL,19,Fthe UK.
